  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/71d09c949402e562e6c88bb366816529.avif?t=1745450635\" width=540 height=172 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Game.</h2><br>The souls of the dead have been trapped in a Purgatory-like dimension where they are forced to fight each other for a chance to escape. Follow the main party as they brave the danger, face exotic enemies, make allies and learn more about the true nature of the competition in their quest to win their freedom back.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/57d5cd7caf53de3e75ea4511f3074ac7.poster.avif?t=1745450635\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/57d5cd7caf53de3e75ea4511f3074ac7.webm?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/57d5cd7caf53de3e75ea4511f3074ac7.mp4?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features.</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/05873e08e380d0458df45215730404ff.poster.avif?t=1745450635\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/05873e08e380d0458df45215730404ff.webm?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/05873e08e380d0458df45215730404ff.mp4?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Active Turn Battle (ATB) combat system.<br></li><li> 3 main characters with unique attributes, skills and upgrades to fit your preferred strategy.<br></li><li> Story driven game.<br></li><li> Pick your fights in the Arena.<br></li><li> Pet a dinosaur. </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/79f911303695c9a7d853bf698a10a98c.poster.avif?t=1745450635\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/79f911303695c9a7d853bf698a10a98c.webm?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/79f911303695c9a7d853bf698a10a98c.mp4?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Demo Available Now!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/fad60b67e29773ecf3084037e64e2897.poster.avif?t=1745450635\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/fad60b67e29773ecf3084037e64e2897.webm?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2488940/extras/fad60b67e29773ecf3084037e64e2897.mp4?t=1745450635\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
